use to use metaobject for faq ques and answer

Here’s a production-ready FAQ section using metaobjects (clean, dynamic, scalable) 💻🔥

🔧 Metaobject Setup (Shopify Admin)
Create metaobject definition:

Name: FAQ

Fields:

question (Single line text)

answer (Rich text)

Then create entries.

🔥 Use Metaobject in Section
sections/faq.liquid
<section class="faq-section">
  <div class="faq-section__container">
    <h2 class="faq-section__title">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h2>

    {% assign faqs = shop.metaobjects.faq.values %}

    {% if faqs != blank %}
      <div class="faq-section__wrapper">
        {% for item in faqs %}
          <div class="faq-section__item">
            <button class="faq-section__question">
              {{ item.question }}
            </button>
            <div class="faq-section__answer">
              {{ item.answer }}
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>

  <style>
    .faq-section {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .faq-section__title {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .faq-section__item {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 15px 0;
    }

    .faq-section__question {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 16px;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      position: relative;
    }

    .faq-section__answer {
      display: none;
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .faq-section__item.active .faq-section__answer {
      display: block;
    }
  </style>

  <script>
    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-section__question').forEach(button => {
      button.addEventListener('click', () => {
        button.parentElement.classList.toggle('active')
      })
    })
  </script>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "FAQ Section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "Frequently Asked Questions"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "FAQ Section"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
